<section id="body">
	<video class="rightFloat" src="../Media/Unit05_e6.flv" mode="1" id="1003"  /><p align="left"><font color="#0000ff"><b>Strategies</b></font>There are always other ways to say things!</p><p align="left">Don't panic if you can't remember a word, or if you feel you are stuck for words.</p><p align="left"><font color="#000000">Remember the following expressions:</font></p><p align="left"><font color="#000000">"I'm not sure what it's called, but it is/looks like/is used for …"</font></p>"I've forgotten what it is in English, but …""It's similar to …, but I don't remember the word."<p align="left"><font color="#000000"><b>We all forget words sometimes. It happens in natural conversations.</b>&#160;<b>Don't let it bother you!</b></font></p>
